  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hey, do you want to ascend there?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Hey you\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Let me give some advice\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Don't waste your time, you'd better just stay in this shelter\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"It suits a coward like you\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/23fa623f258631ddb4279630971bc989.avif?t=1751628673\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras_big/23fa623f258631ddb4279630971bc989.avif?t=1751628673 width=800 height=336 /></span>Countless hardships and trials await you. Spikes everywhere, spinning saw blades, falling platforms, and merciless terrain...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/99372bb7316949f7ff67d5915c0239c2.poster.avif?t=1751628673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/99372bb7316949f7ff67d5915c0239c2.webm?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/99372bb7316949f7ff67d5915c0239c2.mp4?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hmm... Maybe the smoking guy was right. Perhaps it's better to stay in the shelter and not waste your time...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/585e3dd652d2e7657fc43ccfb9e35d98.poster.avif?t=1751628673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/585e3dd652d2e7657fc43ccfb9e35d98.webm?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/585e3dd652d2e7657fc43ccfb9e35d98.mp4?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hmm... Do you still want to Ascend this place? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Then prove it with your actions.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was made by a single person.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frustrated? Don’t worry. Just climb again.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The developer took 30 minutes to clear the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to the friends you meet along the way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A crown awaits at the end...?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming retro-style graphics and sound.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The smoking guy... you might even grow fond of him...?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for the blue hole...!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hey, do you want to ascend there?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Hey you\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Let me give some advice\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"Don't waste your time, you'd better just stay in this shelter\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>\"It suits a coward like you\"</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/23fa623f258631ddb4279630971bc989.avif?t=1751628673\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras_big/23fa623f258631ddb4279630971bc989.avif?t=1751628673 width=800 height=336 /></span>Countless hardships and trials await you. Spikes everywhere, spinning saw blades, falling platforms, and merciless terrain...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/99372bb7316949f7ff67d5915c0239c2.poster.avif?t=1751628673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/99372bb7316949f7ff67d5915c0239c2.webm?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/99372bb7316949f7ff67d5915c0239c2.mp4?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hmm... Maybe the smoking guy was right. Perhaps it's better to stay in the shelter and not waste your time...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/585e3dd652d2e7657fc43ccfb9e35d98.poster.avif?t=1751628673\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/585e3dd652d2e7657fc43ccfb9e35d98.webm?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3503080/extras/585e3dd652d2e7657fc43ccfb9e35d98.mp4?t=1751628673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hmm... Do you still want to Ascend this place? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Then prove it with your actions.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game was made by a single person.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frustrated? Don’t worry. Just climb again.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The developer took 30 minutes to clear the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to the friends you meet along the way!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A crown awaits at the end...?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming retro-style graphics and sound.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The smoking guy... you might even grow fond of him...?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for the blue hole...!</p></li></ul>",
